Text: "I originaly was born in Argentina Rosario  and it was a dream i been manifesting\
  \ to write and document, talk about the spiritual points of views of the Argentine\
  \ compared to the auatrailan. Me been a psychic medium and healer( im on a tv show\
  \ ) i wanted to voice the culture, the earth connection and beauty. The peoples\
  \ large hearts , food , the poverty and how they remain appreciate and in gratude\
  \ each day.\nTo travel write document and change lives is my life pourpose. \nLove\
  \ to go to africa too to meet witch doctors ( which i have access to) \nMeet the\
  \ people and land.\nTo the island and meet sharmans.\nNow days humanity is evolving\
  \ fast and looking towards answers and peace. \nI will be doing a retreat too im\
  \ colombia. \nTeaching and meeting the indigenous there.\nIm in Australia and have\
  \ soo many beautiful place here too."
